ly"," scientific"," principles"," and"," critical"," thinking"," when"," assessing"," such"," claims",","," rather"," than"," jumping"," to"," conclusions"," based"," on"," limited"," evidence"," or"," personal"," beliefs",".","\n\n","Addressing"," this"," issue"," is"," crucial"," because"," it"," directly"," impacts"," public"," understanding"," of"," scientific"," research"," and"," the"," credibility"," of"," scientific"," institutions"," like"," NASA","."," When"," unfounded"," theories"," gain"," traction"," and"," are"," spread"," without"," proper"," scrutiny",","," it"," can"," undermine"," public"," trust"," in"," the"," scientific"," community","."," This"," is"," particularly"," concerning"," in"," an"," age"," where"," misinformation"," spreads"," rapidly"," through"," social"," media"," and"," other"," online"," platforms","."," Therefore",","," it"," is"," important"," for"," scientific"," organizations"," like"," NASA"," to"," continue"," deb","unking"," false"," claims",","," providing"," evidence","-","based"," explanations",","," and"," engaging"," with"," the"," public"," to"," promote"," scientific"," literacy",".","\n\n","One"," solution"," to"," address"," this"," issue"," is"," to"," enhance"," science"," education"," and"," critical"," thinking"," skills","."," By"," promoting"," scientific"," literacy",","," individuals"," will"," be"," better"," equipped"," to"," evaluate"," claims"," based"," on"," evidence"," and"," logical"," reasoning","."," This"," can"," be"," achieved"," through"," educational"," campaigns",","," outreach"," programs",","," and"," incorporating"," critical"," thinking"," skills"," into"," the"," curriculum"," at"," all"," education"," levels",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," belief"," that"," the"," face"," on"," Mars"," was"," created"," by"," aliens"," is"," not"," supported"," by"," scientific"," evidence"," and"," is"," not"," considered"," to"," be"," of"," extrater","restrial"," origin"," by"," NASA"